        All matter in the universe is made from atoms:
        <ul>
            <li>Gases (steam)</li>
            <li>Liquids (water)</li>
            <li>Solids (ice)</li>
        </ul>
        All atoms consist of neutrons, protons and electrons.
        <br>A <strong>molecule</strong> is a group of atoms bonded to each other in a specific pattern.
